OL,3,C'Discoloured water' in North Cornwall
OL,4,Cafter main damaged
OL,6,FResidents in North Cornwall say
OL,7,Fdiscoloured water is still coming out
OL,8,Fof their taps, after the area's water
OL,9,Fnetwork was damaged.
OL,11,FSouth West Water customers across
OL,12,FLaunceston, Tregadillet and the
OL,13,Fsurrounding areas experienced a
OL,14,Ftemporary loss of water supply and low
OL,15,Fpressure on Tuesday, 3 March, after a
OL,16,Fmain in Trebartha was damaged by a
OL,17,Fthird party.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
