PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772640682
OL,3,C'Discoloured water' in North Cornwall
OL,4,Cafter main damaged
OL,6,FThe provider says teams have delivered
OL,7,Fbottled water to its most vulnerable
OL,8,Fcustomers and have worked through the
OL,9,Fnight to deliver water to other
OL,10,Fcustomers on its priority services
OL,11,Fregister.
OL,13,FA bottled water station at Martins
OL,14,FCash and Carry on Pennygillam Way
OL,15,Fstayed open overnight. A second
OL,16,Fstation at Trethorne Leisure Park was
OL,17,Fopen until 10pm on Tuesday, 3 March.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
