CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772640682
OL,3,C'Discoloured water' in North Cornwall
OL,4,Cafter main damaged
OL,6,FIn a statement that night, South West
OL,7,FWater said: "As the water returns, you
OL,8,Fmay notice the water is discoloured.
OL,9,FWe are currently asking customers not
OL,10,Fto run their taps at the moment, and
OL,11,Fwill let customers know when this can
OL,12,Fbe run off.
OL,14,F"We're sorry for the disruption and
OL,15,Fthank you for your patience and
OL,16,Funderstanding. We'll continue to keep
OL,17,Fyou updated."
OL,19,FThe Windmill Hill Academy in
OL,20,FLaunceston has delayed opening until
OL,21,Fat least 10:30am on Wednesday 4 March.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
