PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772640682
OL,3,C'Discoloured water' in North Cornwall
OL,4,Cafter main damaged
OL,6,FAt 7am, it said: "Unfortunately, our
OL,7,Fwater remains discoloured this
OL,8,Fmorning. I am currently awaiting
OL,9,Fupdated advice from South West Water.
OL,11,F"At present, we have been advised not
OL,12,Fto run taps or flush the system until
OL,13,Ffurther instruction is given.
OL,15,F"As a result, school opening has been
OL,16,Fdelayed until 10:30am. Thank you for
OL,17,Fyour continued patience and
OL,18,Funderstanding. I will update you again
OL,19,Fas soon as I have further information."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
